landing pageplanning/*.xlsx
*Lead Capture*.xlsx

# Image source originals — raw material only. Only the optimized .webp ships.
# Source PNG/JPG/zip must never reach the CDN (they were deploying ~7.4 MB of
# unreferenced originals). See docs/sop-image-sourcing.md (performance budget).
public/images/therapists/originals/
public/images/**/*.zip

